 Under the chanter section, which targeting is discussed. There are some really good tips covered there.<br>
  <br>
 I personally keep the MA targeted and assist off of him (find out which mob they &quot;all&quot; supposed to be beating on) and then work on targeting the adds. This does get tougher in tighter quarters, but practice, practice, practice. <br>
 I find this works for me unless the MA switches targets (I usually will ask for that if we are in Chardok (for example) and a named pops (Auditor, Captain)).<br>
 Also a good tank will space out the mobs as much as possible once you start mezzing and I try not to rely on AE mez as much unless I am low on mana.<br>
